You do look a bit alike.

653
00:41:24,250 --> 00:41:26,349
同样又大又亮的眼睛。
Same big, bright eyes.

654
00:41:31,697 --> 00:41:33,158
我说错什么了吗?
Did I say something wrong?

655
00:41:34,964 --> 00:41:35,996
[笑]
[chuckles]

656
00:41:36,669 --> 00:41:38,801
哦,什么都没有。
Uh, nothing.

657
00:41:41,564 --> 00:41:42,937
