we were so buzzed that we'd made it back that we had a couple of beers.

690
00:43:20,003 --> 00:43:21,167
几。
Just a couple.

691
00:43:22,170 --> 00:43:23,532
别那么紧张，你知道的。
Take the edge off, you know.

692
00:43:24,777 --> 00:43:26,777
她急着回家。
She was in such a rush to get home.

693
00:43:27,505 --> 00:43:28,977
她想开车。
She wanted to drive.

694
00:43:29,815 --> 00:43:33,575
