[Natascha] Oh, my God. All right now, you got this.

717
00:46:00,427 --> 00:46:01,492
快来找我。
Just get to me.

718
00:46:03,001 --> 00:46:04,396
好了，亲爱的，我就在这。
All right, honey, I'm right here.

